collectors.titleDetails: (12 total Queries, 10 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT CASE WHEN YEAR(CURDATE()) - YEAR(tgllahir) BETWEEN 18 AND 25 THEN '18-25' WHEN YEAR(CURDATE()) - YEAR(tgllahir) BETWEEN 26 AND 35 THEN '26-35' WHEN YEAR(CURDATE()) - YEAR(tgllahir) BETWEEN 36 AND 45 THEN '36-45' WHEN YEAR(CURDATE()) - YEAR(tgllahir) > 45 THEN '46+' END AS rentang_usia, COUNT(*) AS jumlah FROM `pencaker` GROUP BY `rentang_usia`
SELECT MONTH(tgllahir) AS bulan, jenkel, COUNT(*) AS jumlah FROM pencaker WHERE YEAR(tgllahir) = '2024' GROUP BY MONTH(tgllahir), jenkel ORDER BY MONTH(tgllahir)
